Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要躺在医务室好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要帮忙的话随时说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.43,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:18.07,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:26.96,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:31.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:38.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:42.75,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:50.56,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:55.28,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:07.03,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:14.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:20.12,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.05,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:30.56,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:18.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我们的愿望实现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:26.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍贵的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:31.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:38.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隐藏的伤痕在发冷颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:42.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找寻我的容身之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:50.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在这个遵循常识的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:55.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破无可救药的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:07.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封闭的心灵正发出呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:14.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:20.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们几乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要暧昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:30.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}只需去追寻真切的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 随时都能上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边也OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 艾丽西娅她…重伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是被枪击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事很蹊跷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被枪击说明附近潜伏着帝国的狙击手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么挑艾丽西娅这样普通女兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事现在不重要！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去艾丽西娅那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾丽西娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗击帝国保护艾丽西娅是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们现在应该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还等什么 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们用自己的双手把帝国军赶出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意 目标只有突前的女武神一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用理会后方的坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么 那样的炮击下毫发无伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火 开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别只顾着看 疏忽了驾驶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保持一定距离 否则难保不被殃及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那正所谓一骑当千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有万夫不当之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的掩护也是多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告 帝国军女武神突破第一道防线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续向这里推进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此轻易突破了我们的防线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中女武神族的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据闻科迪莉亚公主也继承了女武神族血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对女武神之矛和神盾就是最好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请您施展女武神的神力为我们而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军 请镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我镇定着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亚公主 您是我们唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰扎特少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有女武神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 你是哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义勇军第一小队队长 法尔迪奥·兰扎特少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把女武神的矛与盾借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区义勇军小队长想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还妄称拥有女武神的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事给我们解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰扎特少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亚公主 请稍许忍耐片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 清醒下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借矛与盾一用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 别追
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 为什么不追
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拦住他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事 请交给我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解释给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科…科迪莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于梅尔姬沃特中士的伤情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呈现出异常的恢复速度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉请出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其肉体一旦濒临死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会觉醒成为战斗种族 女武神族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过迅速的恢复 唤醒其真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承女武神血脉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 暂时撤退到第三道防线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二道防线也被突破了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 抵达第三道防线也只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底干什么吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是女武神 也不过就一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亚公主的事打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义勇军说过会负责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要多管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么偏偏这种时候 一件事接着一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫不得已时只能全军撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 给他们点颜色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:12:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅身负重伤的消息或许会有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难为他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要在这里挡住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们来保护艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的士兵说女武神有矛和盾在手刀枪不入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接攻击可能会有效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能尝试多方向同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 艾丽西娅 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神逼近第三道防线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍 女武神逼近第三道防线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我…我该怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 艾丽西娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要还击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持弹幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她全力防御时应该无法轻易反击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从多个方向持续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神的神力也有极限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在分散移动包围赛尔贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来点支援炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看炮 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说不需要我们帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险 差点见阎王了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让人怎么打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心 我们阻止不了那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋整啊 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 回到最终防线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和后方队伍汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要离开Edelweiss号太远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 听得到吗 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法尔迪奥 就在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 我求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告 第三道防线陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小队 立刻撤退至最终防线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 第三道防线陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小队 立刻撤退至最终防线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那是维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正身处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救他 去救救维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告加利亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻放下武器投降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许胡说 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位姑娘是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神族？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么 干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亚也有女武神族 从没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击 集中火力攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉…厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是艾丽西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上不需要两个女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火 给我开火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerbil开炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…什么家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会发展成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 全军撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是艾丽西娅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅…你这是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太过悲伤的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默数着星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早该习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾独自将你找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我愿心中只思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不愿忘却这悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}仅此而已 唯有此心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}是的 那是唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======NEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫荷马·皮耶洛尼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我这样的人会加入义勇军？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 我也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一明白的是 艰苦的战斗中也会有幸福的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 战场女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第22章 困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱者因脆弱而知坚强为何物
